# BKG Blocker Dashboard Rules

When a blocker is detected:
1. Dashboard opens/updates automatically
2. Current blocker, agent positions, and vote table are displayed
3. User can Approve, Reject, or Request Revision
4. TTS can read the current blocker summary aloud
5. Fourth voice API can be called for external review

API endpoints:
- GET /api/state
- POST /api/blocker
- POST /api/rat/start
- POST /api/vote
- POST /api/user/approve
- POST /api/user/reject
- POST /api/tts/read
